\par {\listtext\pard\plain\fcs1 \af0 \fcs0 \f3\fs20\insrsid15551003 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Retry: Any 
conditions that apply to successive attempts to use the skill successfully. If this paragraph is omitted, the skill can be retried without any inherent penalty other than consuming additional time.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\fcs1 \af0 \fcs0 \f3\fs20\insrsid15551003 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Special: Any extra facts that apply to the skill, such a
s rules regarding untrained use, or if this skill has a synergistic relationship with other skills, or benefits that certain characters receive because of class or race.
\par }\pard\plain \s17\ql \li0\ri0\sb100\sa100\sbauto1\saauto1\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fcs1 \af0\afs24\alang60488 \fcs0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\fcs1 \af0 \fcs0 \ul\insrsid15551003 
